{"tid":694450,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[一房一千萬］北角柏蔚山加推  1房折實1434.3萬起","createTime":"2018-06-08T10:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T11:40:01.000Z","uid":55257,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cc613939ed5ed291e7b1919d41714ab6a97ab74f","tid":694450,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T10:32:14.000Z","msg":"新世界牽頭的北角柏蔚山加推第5張價單共100伙，首推1房單位，折實1,434.3萬起。發展商料短期內上載銷售安排，預料最快下周展開次輪銷售。<br />\n<br />\n整批100伙由1房至4房不等，價單定價1,792.9萬元至8,461.5萬元，價單呎價32,122至56,532元。扣除即供最高折扣，折實1,434.3萬至6,769.2萬，折實呎價25,698至最高45,225元。<br />\n<br />\n今次新推單位有51伙1房單位，其中3座6樓D室，實用面積548平方呎，折實1434.3萬元，呎價26,173元。<br />\n<br />\n項目今再沽出最後一伙可售3房一套戶，為3座27樓C室，實用面積798平方呎，成交價27,43.8萬元，呎價為34,383元，項目累售238伙，佔可售單位約96%，套現逾58億元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ps.hket.com/article/2089962\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2089962&d=ZvXTksCwc%2BfYe7yVSMZDym6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=52b96b06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ps.hket.com/article/2089962</a>"},{"pid":"20bdd9047e4679fb1092c0087fdf0bc3e25b4311","tid":694450,"uid":84633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T11:18:58.000Z","msg":"唔明點解賣到咁貴<br />\n<br />\n北角咋咼？<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳都係20,000一呎啫"},{"pid":"af19e1b39a8ffc7a71f046c23c49f87a782c11d2","tid":694450,"uid":161924,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"20bdd9047e4679fb1092c0087fdf0bc3e25b4311","tid":694450,"uid":84633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T11:18:58.000Z","msg":"唔明點解賣到咁貴<br />\n<br />\n北角咋咼？<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳都係20,000一呎啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T11:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3fa22756893b642b4d57021feea4f27c91095cd","tid":694450,"uid":20072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T11:25:49.000Z","msg":"北角都不知幾正,去邊都方便"},{"pid":"82fb2629bd957d8bd1f8071b9ced5df192612215","tid":694450,"uid":19676,"like":1,"dislike":0,